column5: Second swim back and my shoulder was much better. I did a pyramid swim with 50m, 100m, 200m, 400m, 200m, 100m and 50m for a total of 1.1k.

First swim in about a year. My shoulder has been very sore and at first I didn't think it was going to work out because swimming was extremely painful. However, as the session went on, my shoulder loosened up an I got to the point where I swam 250m continuously although my edit arm wasn't contributing much.
